Hear us review the latest Marvel movie that has fans and not fans alike talking! Multiverse of Madness was a hell of a thrill ride but did it meet expectations? What are the implications for the rest of the Marvel Universe? Is YOUR third eye open? Some of these questions and more will be answered in this SPOILER-FILLED REVIEW of Doctor Strange in The Multiverse of Madness. Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

